blackdoor.cqbe.keystore

Class KeyStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • blackdoor.cqbe.keystore.KeyStore

  • public class KeyStore
extends java.lang.Object
    This Class handles the file io, encryption and retrieval of all keys from the default/configured store location for a user's private keys.

    Version:
    v0.0.1 - Nov 5, 2014
    Author:
    Cj Buresch
